to know , learn and get all things come and join here

https://forum.suprbay.org/member.php?action=register&referrer=126762
I created a key file with the keygen, registered it, but it STILL "reminds" me at every startup to buy it. Why?

I also have that problem! I make a licence with the keymaker and activate it but when I refresh or restart it keeps reminding me to "Buy Rainlendar Licence" in Events!
It's really anoying, but no mater what name and mail I put in the keymaker and generate licence it's still up and buging!
I have the same problem. any adivce?
C'mon man write something to help the situation! I tried everything!

Not Working!
I have the same problem. I install everything and generate a license file, but the program keeps "Reminding me to buy the full version"
It looks as if the license is valid till 01.01.2012.

Don't care any more! I exported my list to .csv and .ics files and uninstalled the "Pro" version. Then I downloaded free Lite version from official web and installed it. Inported .ics and all is well once again. It has minor limitations but I use it without them anyway.
When you can't beat them, join them! :)
